videos.description: Less than a minute into their game, Kyle Lowry lobs a pass up to Jonas Valanciunas who completely misses the rim and throws the ball off the backboard.

videos.headline: Raptors open game with awful alley-oop attempt

videos.description: Tony Allen intercepts a pass and races down the court before giving off to Troy Williams for the transition dunk.

videos.headline: Allen's stout defense leads to transition dunk

videos.description: JaMychal Green comes down with a rebound, and surrounded by a plethora of Raptors defenders, Green is able to throw up a hook shot that goes in, all while being fouled.
